  "prompt": "What are the things you can do on your 23rd Birthday?",
  "response": "Here are some fun things you can do on your 23rd birthday:\n\n1. Go out with friends\n- Dinner party\n- Bar or club celebration\n- House party\n\n2. Travel\n- Weekend trip\n- Day trip to a nearby city\n- Short vacation\n\n3. Personal experiences\n- Try a new adventure activity\n- Take a cooking class\n- Go skydiving or bungee jumping\n\n4. Milestone activities\n- Start a savings plan\n- Update career goals\n- Reflect on personal growth\n\n5. Entertainment\n- Watch a concert\n- Go to a comedy show\n- Movie marathon\n- Attend a sporting event\n\n6. Social activities\n- Group celebration\n- Organize a themed party\n- Have a game night\n\n7. Self-care\n- Spa day\n- Personal photoshoot\n- Treat yourself to something special\n\n8. Family celebration\n- Family dinner\n- Gather with relatives\n- Shared family activity\n\n9. Creative pursuits\n- Start a new hobby\n- Take a workshop\n- Learn a new skill\n\n10. Personal milestone celebrations\n- Create a bucket list\n- Set personal goals\n- Document your journey\n\nRemember, the best way to celebrate is to do something that makes you happy and feels meaningful to you.",
